    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款第一人称点击冒险游戏，背景设定在充满复古未来感的末日世界，巨型昆虫和废弃机器人统治一切。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301420/extras/d68595fcc585507e506ecc69b260fdc6.poster.avif?t=1771927111\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301420/extras/d68595fcc585507e506ecc69b260fdc6.webm?t=1771927111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301420/extras/d68595fcc585507e506ecc69b260fdc6.mp4?t=1771927111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请慢慢探索，寻找你的道路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301420/extras/dedf4b48debb5aea2db7359997ca4c3f.poster.avif?t=1771927111\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301420/extras/dedf4b48debb5aea2db7359997ca4c3f.webm?t=1771927111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301420/extras/dedf4b48debb5aea2db7359997ca4c3f.mp4?t=1771927111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将特定物品组合在一起，创造新的物品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301420/extras/58a2e37e0efa61d452c254c741b18c11.poster.avif?t=1771927111\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301420/extras/58a2e37e0efa61d452c254c741b18c11.webm?t=1771927111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301420/extras/58a2e37e0efa61d452c254c741b18c11.mp4?t=1771927111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拾取可以在后续场景中使用的物品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301420/extras/ad73b46788a941562f212d658b94c16f.poster.avif?t=1771927111\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301420/extras/ad73b46788a941562f212d658b94c16f.webm?t=1771927111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301420/extras/ad73b46788a941562f212d658b94c16f.mp4?t=1771927111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301420/extras/9f824f3684e2b46805ecf76763cea1a1.poster.avif?t=1771927111\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301420/extras/9f824f3684e2b46805ecf76763cea1a1.webm?t=1771927111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301420/extras/9f824f3684e2b46805ecf76763cea1a1.mp4?t=1771927111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301420/extras/c20630d0df09fd6ddc16e131c91a789b.poster.avif?t=1771927111\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301420/extras/c20630d0df09fd6ddc16e131c91a789b.webm?t=1771927111\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301420/extras/c20630d0df09fd6ddc16e131c91a789b.mp4?t=1771927111\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >引人入胜的故事情节，邀请你探索并了解世界的秘密与历史，包括通过收集日记中的绘画页来发现传说。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏特色<br>沉浸式的场景，配以逼真的音效。<br>将鼠标悬停在场景中的隐藏物品上时，会显示动画光标。<br>点击互动对象时，会显示一幅手绘草图，示意预期的操作。<br>收集物品，以便在其他场景中使用。<br>将物品拖放到特定位置以触发动作。<br>通过玩家的操作触发电影序列，推动剧情发展并解锁新区域。<br>在背包中直接组合某些物品以解谜。</p>",
